T02TD3464E:118a-5: drug pa'i lnga pa'i sa bon lnga pa'i dbyangs kyis nye bar mdzes pa stong pa'i lhas mnan pa /
T02TD3464E:118a-6: de las de bzhin du skyes pa'i dpal ldan dkar po 'jam pa'i dbyangs gzhon nu zur phud lnga dang ldan pa /
T02TD3464E:118a-7: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02TD3464E:118a-8: phyag gnyis pa g-yon na autpa la bsnams pa /
T02TD3464E:118a-9: g-yas pa rol pa'i stabs kyis seng ge'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
T02TD3464E:118a-10: bdag nyid gzhon nu'i skur bsam par bya'o //
T02TD3464E:118a-11: 'di'i phyag rgya ni lag pa gnyis thal mo sbyar nas mdzub mo dang ming med dag bkab pa'o //
T02TD3464E:118a-16: aom w'a g'i shva ri mum /
T02TD3464E:118a-17: 'jam dpal gyi sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
